  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nIt is a out-of-bounds read vulnerability in MP4 processing.   \n  \n**VERSION**   \nAdobe Flash Player  23.0.0.207  \nOther versions may be affected too  \n  \n**REPRODUCTION CASE**   \nput LoadMP42.swf and FG-VD-16-088_PoC.mp4 on a server and load http://127.0.0.1:8080/LoadMP4"
